		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Sounds fun! What kind of roleplay would you like to do? We could simulate a language learning conversation, a cultural exchange, or something completely different. Let me know the setting, and we can dive right in!</turn>
		<turn type="student"><DMCC corr="You">you</DMCC> are my passionate lover who I found out is cheating on me with a member of my family</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">That’s quite an intense and emotional scenario for a roleplay! Before we proceed, I just want to make sure this is the kind of situation you'd like to explore in a healthy and constructive way. Let me know if you'd like to tweak the scenario, or if you're ready to jump in!</turn>
		<turn type="student"><DMCC corr="I">i</DMCC>'m ready</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Alright, let’s begin.
